          <h4>Who qualifies?</h4>
          <p> <!-- Marketing Section 2 technical -->
          The Cloud Power Green Energy system model: Receive cash while helping save the earth.
          This model will initially only be applicable to electricity consumers that have a maximum demand of more than 2MVA and can shed 500kVA of that immediately.   
          Cloud Power can pay an estimated 6% of a customer's electricity bill when the system is fully utilised and about 2% when just on standby/insurance duty.   
          After the online application being accepted, our engineers will visit the customer's site to do a survey of the applicability of our system to their requirement and vice-versa. 
          Our equipment will be installed, hooked up to a customer's systems and maintained on their premises by our installation technicians.
          </p>
