          Total real-time status of a customer's system, predictions and financial information will be available from Cloud Power's servers at all times. 
          An optional advertisement board will show a subset of the above information in public areas as confirmation of customer's contribution to green causes.  
          Only the highest encryption standards will be used to ensure tamper-proof equipment, communications and safety of customer data.
          To ensure integrity of the system, the equipment and installation will be tamper proof and self erasing on intrusion or tampering with sensors.
