          <p>
          The payments start immediately when our system comes online and could be 1% to 2% of your electricity bill while it is just on standby. 
          This increases to between five and eight percent of the bill if all available electricity is sold, thus when an estimated 25% of your maximum demand is shed during peak periods. 
          The equipment monitors the total and switched load on your premises continuously and determines the energy switched off in a transparent way. 
          The maximum switch off period is limited to two hours in any 12-hour period with a maximum of four shed periods, of at least half hour each, in the same period.
          All the financial transactions use Bitcoin thus there are very low transaction fees and balances will be settled daily.
          A supply/insurance contract between the electricity customer and us will be set up for an initial 3-year period.
